DC_TR_SETUP_REJ_TC5
This is a IBW test case for hardware types that cannot be used in DC_TR_SETUP_REJ_TC4. This test case only assumes that maxIBW is at least twice the size of the smallest supported carrier BW, and that the total bandwidth is at least maxIBW+600kHz. This still means that hardwares that have maxIBW equal to total frequency bandwidth cannot be run.
